  "Filter help": "",
  "Filters allow you to specify which save files you want to include as part of your grail. The filters are written as a space separated list of words which must appear in the save file name.": "",
  "Remember to include the \"sharedstash\" file if you want shared stash items to be checked! For example, \"mule sharedstash\" will include all save files containing the words \"mule\" or \"sharedstash\", with case insensitive matching.": "",
  "You can also exclude save files which contain a certain word, by prefixing it with an exclamation mark. For example, \"mule !oldmule\" will include all save files containing the word \"mule\", but exclude any containing \"oldmule\".": "",
  "When the saved games filter is left empty, the filtering feature is disabled and all saved games are checked.": "",
